dmca.title: Software DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google: Android Market

works.description:
Goal tracking application.  I used a  
freelancer to write my code  
(http://www.freelancer.com/projects/Mobile-Phone-Android/Simple-Goal-Tracking-Android-App.html).
  
He signed a non-disclosure agreement, then two weeks later this app  
appeared on the market.  It has the exact same features requested in my
app  
and only the freelancer had access to the feature requests.
